  "2026-07-05T19:56:01.285Z",codex-agent,"Greptile follow-up: addressed P1 direct runAction list status filtering by making runMcpListAction read nested options.status when top-level status is absent; simplified PmClient.list/search to pass one nested options bag; added SDK regression coverage for runAction({ action: 'list', options: { status } }). Re-verified: focused SDK/MCP tests, pnpm typecheck, pnpm lint, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage at 100/100/100/100."
  "2026-07-05T20:20:00.428Z",codex-agent,"Greptile follow-up: fixed remaining branch review findings by inlining the MCP handler lookup in src/mcp/server.ts and deactivating workspace extension activations after SDK runtime contract registration loading. Added regression coverage proving getWorkspaceContracts triggers activate/deactivate for schema extensions. Verification after follow-up: focused SDK/MCP tests passed (156 tests), pnpm typecheck passed, pnpm lint passed (ESLint, jscpd 0 clones, static quality gate), and full coverage passed with 264 files, 5424 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines."
  "2026-07-05T20:40:12.050Z",codex-agent,"CodeQL follow-up: replaced normalizeActionName regex sanitization in src/sdk/runtime.ts with a linear scanner to avoid polynomial-regex risk on uncontrolled action names, and added MCP regression coverage for repeated separator normalization. Verification after CodeQL fix: focused SDK/MCP tests passed (156 tests), pnpm typecheck passed, pnpm lint passed, and full coverage passed with 264 files, 5424 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines."
